{"tid":2312567,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國國務院突終止五項中美交流計劃   一項涉及香港","createTime":"2020-12-05T05:23:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T08:40:36.000Z","uid":39464,"like":39,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6544d6580813861f4f9f868f40a8a582de6e088e","tid":2312567,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T05:23:49.000Z","msg":"中美角力進一步升溫，國務院周五突終止五項中國資助的中美交流計劃，國務院形容計劃以交流為名，實則是北京宣傳軟實力的工具，其中一項涉及香港。美國國務卿蓬佩奧周五發表聲明，指他已向打壓異見的中國官員及其他人士，實施入境美國的簽證限制。蓬佩奧同日在中東一個會議演說，亦警惕中國威脅，提醒中東各國切勿淪為附庸國，又形容目前中美角力非中美之爭，而是自由與暴政之爭。<br />\n<br />\n叫停的計劃包括「政策制定人士中國教育旅行計劃」（Policymakers Educational China Trip Program）、「美中友誼計劃」（U.S.-China Friendship Program）、「美中領導者交流計劃」（U.S.-China Leadership Exchange Program）、「美中跨太平洋交流計劃」（U.S.-China Transpacific Exchange Program）及「香港教育與文化計劃」（Hong Kong Educational and Cultural Program）。蓬佩奧指出，上述計劃是依據美國1961年「相互教育與文化交流法」（Mutual Educational and Cultural Exchange Act, MECEA）進行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201205/AVNQS5CIKFGHHNRXK4CNUMILZE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201205%2FAVNQS5CIKFGHHNRXK4CNUMILZE%2F&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1w6Ggm0NOSfkDZSs230CVm%2Fs%3D&h=c6bdb2b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201205%2FAVNQS5CIKFGHHNRXK4CNUMILZE%2F&h=68bcc30f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201205/AVNQS5CIKFGHHNRXK4CNUMILZE/</a>"},{"pid":"380632e3967b43dc38a1fb8004d830d495e48b45","tid":2312567,"uid":54125,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T05:30:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />斷交進行中"},{"pid":"d62b1570b37730fd181fbfcaddb485972274d184","tid":2312567,"uid":127575,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T05:31:56.000Z","msg":"有拜登<br />\n即刻復活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登左膠講吓兩句啦"